edu.mines.jtk.interp

Class RadialInterpolator2.Biharmonic

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.mines.jtk.interp.RadialInterpolator2.Biharmonic
  • Enclosing class:
    RadialInterpolator2

    public static class RadialInterpolator2.Biharmonic
extends java.lang.Object
    Sandwell's biharmonic basis function g(r) = r*r*(log(r)-1).

    A scale factor s may be specified that divides all distances r, so that the basis function becomes g(r/s).

    See Sandwell, 1987, Biharmonic spline interpolation of GEOS-3 and SEASAT altimeter data: Geophysical research letters, 14, 139-142.
